Intelligent Document Reader
Get Intelligent Document Reader to easily extract unstructured content and tables from documents, excluding rows you need not save.

Optimize Data Extraction by Excluding Rows in Tabular Data
Exclude rows during tabular data extraction that you do not need to save by using the new Skip record option in the Intelligent Document Reader. Gain better control over the extraction process to capture only the relevant information.
title: Optimizing Data Extraction with Salesforce's Intelligent Document Reader
